songs.title: Guap
songs.lyrics:

Dexter

I'm never lackin' or lurkin'
Wait, walk in the mall and I spent 50 Gs
I fell in love with the cheese (I did)
I got your bitch on her knees
Boy, you don't wanna beef

Niggas, they love to hate, pass me the Fanta, Jay
Killin' rappers, on a rampage, my diamonds cut you, get a Band-Aid
Yeah, we gotta hear you niggas, pull out the brand new Bentley

[Chorus: KILLY]
